\"ngram\": \"demand\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlikethe opening ceremony, which took place on the River Seine, the closing ceremony will be held on dry land at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Unlikethe opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"dry land\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As is tradition, it will feature the athletes' parade, a medal presentation ceremony, and a thank you for volunteers.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tradition\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' parade\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal presentation ceremony\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"volunteers\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kaylee McKeown and Matt Wearn - who have both won gold medals at this year's Games - will lead the Australian delegation as flag bearers at the closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kaylee McKeown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q